### Hint

To see which option is selected, read the properties of its parent: **value** gives you the value of the selected option (as displayed in the HTML), **selectedIndex** gives you the 0-based index of the selected option. E.g. if miles are selected, **#inputUnits.value** is &quot; **mi**&quot;, **#inputUnits.selectedIndex** is **4**. Option text is irrelevant.
